<Body>
	<Title>新加坡137人食物中毒两人死亡</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年4月9日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">中新网</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">4月8日</Time>综合外电<Denoter did="d1" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>，</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Location lid="l2">新加坡</Location>发生集体<Denoter did="d2" type="emergency">食物中毒</Denoter>事件</Event>，<Event eid="e3"><Participant sid="s3">137人</Participant>在<Denoter did="d3" type="action">食用</Denoter>了当地一种很受欢迎的<Object oid="o3">色拉</Object></Event>后<Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e5">其中<Participant sid="s5">2人</Participant><Denoter did="d5" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e6"><Participant sid="s6">新加坡卫生部发言人</Participant><Denoter did="d6" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e7"><Participant sid="s7,s8,s9">一名59岁的妇女</Participant>在<Time tid="t7" type="relTime">上周五</Time><Denoter did="d7" type="action">食用</Denoter>了<Object oid="o7">“rojak”</Object>(马来西亚色拉)</Event>后<Event eid="e8"><Denoter did="d8" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e9">于<Time tid="t9" type="relTime">8日</Time>不治<Denoter did="d9" type="stateChange">身亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e10">另<Participant sid="s10">一名57岁的妇女</Participant>在<Time tid="t10" type="relTime">6日</Time><Denoter did="d10" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e11"><Denoter did="d11" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e12">在<Denoter did="d12" type="action">食用</Denoter>了<Object oid="o12">有毒色拉</Object></Event>后，<Event eid="e13"><Participant sid="s13">中毒者</Participant><Denoter did="d13" type="stateChange">出现</Denoter>腹部痉挛、呕吐和腹泻<Object oid="o13">现象</Object></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>此次事件被当地媒体描述为该国历史上最严重的食物中毒事件。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14">新加坡卫生部长</Participant><Denoter did="d14" type="statement">称</Denoter></Event>，这起事件牵涉到100多人，是严重的问题。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e15"><Participant sid="s15">当局</Participant>会<Denoter did="d15" type="operation">彻查</Denoter><Object oid="o15">事发原因</Object></Event>，他希望事件能提醒国人注意卫生的重要性。</Sentence></Paragraph>
 
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e16"><Time tid="t16" type="relTime">目前</Time>仍有<Participant sid="s16">30多人</Participant>接受<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">住院治疗</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e17">其余<Participant sid="s17">100人</Participant><Denoter did="d17" type="emergency">中毒</Denoter>迹象较轻</Event>，不用住院。</Sentence></Paragraph>
